why are there 5000 players here

music from:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC9UKPs9ZisfhMJdalnETLRg (tons of the music I use is by AZALI so check him out!)

This is a Minecraft video recorded in the Unstable Universe / Unstable SMP that is staged for story-telling purposes; any more staged videos I upload will have a disclaimer in the description saying that they are also staged. Also, a lot of the game mechanics/glitches/redstone discussed in Unstable SMP videos are unique to the Unstable SMP / Unstable Universe and either will not work the same/do not exist in vanilla Minecraft.

snippet.title: Return to Silent Hill - Official Trailer (2026) Hannah Emily Anderson, Jeremy Irvine, Robert Strange
snippet.description:
Watch the Official Trailer for Return to Silent Hill, an upcoming action horror film distributed by Konami and Cineverse. Witness the thriller that's inspired by the iconic video game franchise with Return to Silent Hill, in theaters on January 23, 2026.

When a mysterious letter calls him back to Silent Hill searching for his lost love, James finds a once-recognizable town and encounters figures both familiar and new and begins to question his own sanity.

Return to Silent Hill stars Hannah Emily Anderson, Jeremy Irvine, Robert Strange, Evie Templeton, Pearse Egan, Eve Macklin, Emily Carding, and more. The film is directed by Christophe Gans and written by Christophe Gans, Hiroyuki Owaku, and William Josef Schneider. 

Return to Silent Hill is in theaters on January 23, 2026.

snippet.title: STRANGER THINGS 5: FINAL TRAILER | One Last Adventure | Netflix
snippet.description:
#Netflix #StrangerThings #StrangerThings5

üé• Attention viewers! (ITS FAN MADE)
Enter the final chapter of the Hawkins saga with this Stranger Things Season 5 concept trailer, featuring the return of Eleven, Chief Hopper, Mike, Will, Dustin, Lucas, Max, Jonathan, Joyce, Steve, and the entire cast you love. As Vecna rises stronger than ever, the group faces their last and most dangerous battle in Netflix‚Äôs epic conclusion. Starring Millie Bobby Brown, Finn Wolfhard, Noah Schnapp, Caleb McLaughlin, Sadie Sink, Gaten Matarazzo, Maya Hawke, Joe Keery, Natalia Dyer, Charlie Heaton, Cara Buono, Winona Ryder, David Harbour, and Jamie Campbell Bower, this Stranger Things 5 Final Season Trailer imagines the end of the Upside Down like never before.

The inspiration behind this video:
The Stranger Things Season 5 Trailer delivers the most intense look yet at the final chapter of Netflix‚Äôs global phenomenon. As Stranger Things Season 5 rises to its epic conclusion, the story pushes Eleven, Mike Wheeler, Will Byers, Dustin, Lucas, Max, Jonathan Byers, Joyce Byers, and Chief Hopper toward their most dangerous fight. With the Stranger Things 5 Final Season Trailer 2 and the highly anticipated Stranger Things 5 Official Teaser, fans get a powerful preview of the darkness returning to Hawkins.

Featuring the full returning cast‚Äîincluding Millie Bobby Brown, Finn Wolfhard, Noah Schnapp, Caleb McLaughlin, Sadie Sink, Gaten Matarazzo, Maya Hawke, Joe Keery, Natalia Dyer, Charlie Heaton, Cara Buono, Winona Ryder, and David Harbour‚Äîthe final season raises the stakes to an unprecedented level. Vecna, played by Jamie Campbell Bower, looms larger than ever, turning Hawkins into a battleground that threatens the world. Meanwhile, Steve Harrington and the rest of the group prepare for a final stand with emotional depth, high tension, and the cinematic scale that defines Netflix‚Äôs biggest series.

Stay tuned for more coverage from Rotten Tomatoes TV, Teaser PRO, FilmSpot Trailer, MovieGasm, KinoCheck, EmergencyAwesome, IGN TV Trailer, and TV Promos, as they break down every teaser, cast reveal, and trailer release. Whether you're following new updates from Netflix or revisiting character arcs, this is the ultimate place to explore everything shaping the final season of Stranger Things.

‚óñMade/Edited By Us‚óó
(SFX, VFX, Art) 
‚ñ∫ Art by TeaserCon IG:  /teaserconofficial
‚óñAttention viewers‚óó This Film & Animation video created only for Entertainment. 
Most of VFX created by us.

Thank You So Much For Watching!
Subscribe Now For More.

Stranger Things is an American science fiction horror drama television series created by the Duffer Brothers for Netflix. Produced by Monkey Massacre Productions and 21 Laps Entertainment, the first season was released on Netflix on July 15, 2016. The second and third season followed in October 2017 and July 2019 respectively, and the fourth season aired in two parts in May and July 2022. In February 2022, Stranger Things was renewed for a fifth and final season.
Set in the 1980s, the series centers around the residents of the fictional small town of Hawkins, Indiana, as they are plagued by a hostile alternate dimension known as the Upside Down, after a nearby human experimentation facility opens a gateway between it and the normal world. The ensemble cast includes Winona Ryder, David Harbour, Finn Wolfhard, Millie Bobby Brown, Gaten Matarazzo, Caleb McLaughlin, Natalia Dyer, Charlie Heaton, Cara Buono, Matthew Modine, Noah Schnapp, Sadie Sink, Joe Keery, Dacre Montgomery, Sean Astin, Paul Reiser, Maya Hawke, Priah Ferguson and Brett Gelman. Stranger Things trailer concept, Stranger Things Season 5, Stranger Things Season 5 trailer,  The Duffer Brothers developed Stranger Things as a mix of investigative drama and supernatural elements portrayed with horror and childlike sensibilities, while infusing references to the pop culture of the 1980s. Several thematic and directorial elements were inspired by the works of Steven Spielberg, John Carpenter, David Lynch, Stephen King, Wes Craven and H. P. Lovecraft. They also took inspiration from experiments conducted during the Cold War and conspiracy theories involving secret government programs.
One of Netflix's flagship series, Stranger Things has attracted record viewership on the streaming platform. Stranger Things Season 5 teaser trailer.It has been critically acclaimed for its characterization, atmosphere, acting, soundtrack, directing, writing, and homages to 1980s films. It has received numerous nominations and awards. An animated spin-off series, developed by Eric Robles and produced by Flying Bark Productions, is in development.

snippet.title: Five Nights at Freddy's 2 | A First Look
snippet.description:
Taking it to a whole new level. Five Nights at Freddy‚Äôs 2 only in theaters December 5. Get tickets now: https://www.fivenightsatfreddys.movie/


In 2023, Blumhouse‚Äôs box-office horror phenomenon Five Nights at Freddy‚Äôs, based on the blockbuster game series by Scott Cawthon, became the highest-grossing horror film of the year. Now, a shocking new chapter of animatronic terror begins. 
 
One year has passed since the supernatural nightmare at Freddy Fazbear‚Äôs Pizza. The stories about what transpired there have been twisted into a campy local legend, inspiring the town‚Äôs first ever Fazfest. 
 
Former security guard Mike (Josh Hutcherson) and police officer Vanessa (Elizabeth Lail) have kept the truth from Mike‚Äôs 11-year-old sister, Abby (Piper Rubio), concerning the fate of her animatronic friends. 
 
But when Abby sneaks out to reconnect with Freddy, Bonnie, Chica, and Foxy, it will set into motion a terrifying series of events, revealing dark secrets about the true origin of Freddy‚Äôs, and unleashing a long-forgotten horror hidden away for decades.
 
The cast of Five Nights at Freddy‚Äôs 2 includes returning co-stars Theodus Crane as Jeremiah and the legendary Matthew Lillard as William Afton. The film features new characters played by Freddy Carter (Shadow and Bone, Pennyworth), Wayne Knight (Jurassic Park, Seinfeld), Mckenna Grace (Ghostbusters franchise, Annabelle Comes Home) and horror icon Skeet Ulrich (Scream, Riverdale). 
 
Five Nights at Freddy‚Äôs 2 is directed by acclaimed returning filmmaker Emma Tammi and is written by game series creator Scott Cawthon.
 
The film is produced by Blumhouse founder and CEO Jason Blum and Scott Cawthon, who together produced the first film. The executive producers are director Emma Tammi, Beatriz Sequeira, Christopher Warner, Russell Binder and Marc Mostman. 
 
The first Freddy‚Äôs film opened to a record-shattering $80 million in October 2023 and went on to earn almost $300 million worldwide.

snippet.title: I Hosted a Unique Pokemon Tournament
snippet.description:
I Hosted a Tournament where every single Pokemon was unique. This is Pokemon Draft League, a special type of ruleset where the better a Pokemon is, the more expensive it becomes - and niche Pokemon you'd rarely see become superstars when the moment is right.

Big thanks to Brian David Gilbert for helping with the stats: https://www.youtube.com/@briandavidgilbert

snippet.title: Vendetta | New Hero Gameplay Trailer | Overwatch 2
snippet.description:
You think you can outrun the wolf? That‚Äôs cute.

Introducing Vendetta - Overwatch‚Äôs first-ever melee Damage Hero! With her Palatine Fang greatsword in hand, along with her lightning-fast mobility, Vendetta dominates close-range encounters with raw power and unparalleled precision.

Dash in and demolish your foes using Whirlwind Dash, Soaring Slice, and Projected Edge, all while building attack and movement speed through her Onslaught passive. And when you‚Äôre ready to deliver the final blow, her Sundering Blade Ultimate deals severe damage to enemies directly in front of you.

Claim your vengeance as Vendetta during her limited-time Hero Trial Nov 26 - Dec 1, and see what the future holds for our newest Hero when she officially arrives in Season 20 on Dec 9.

Overwatch 2 is free to play for everyone on console & PC!
_

snippet.title: The Mandalorian And Grogu - First Trailer "Chewbacca" | Star Wars | May 22, 2026
snippet.description:
#themandalorian #leakedtrailer #starwarscelebration  

Watch the 'FAN (CONCEPT) Trailer Concept' For Star Wars The Mandalorian And Grogu (2026)  (More Info About This Video Down Below!)

‚ñ∂Ô∏è Watch More Concept Trailers:

SOLO 2: A Star Wars Story Trailer - https://youtu.be/vCmBvA1j68I üëà

AHSOKA Season 2 Trailer -  https://youtu.be/jQ289yp9c6o üëà

Crimson Dawn : A Star Wars Story Trailer -  https://youtu.be/GtKwWMqrjV8 üëà

"The Mandalorian & Grogu (2026)" marks the Mandalorian saga‚Äôs thrilling return to the big screen under the visionary direction of Jon Favreau, with a screenplay co-written by Favreau and Dave Filoni. This highly anticipated film transports fan-favorite duo Din Djarin and Grogu from their Disney+ appearances into a cinematic scale adventure. Pedro Pascal reprises his role as the stoic Din Djarin, while Grogu continues to captivate audiences through a blend of animatronics, puppetry, and advanced visual effects.

Joining Pascal and Grogu is an esteemed ensemble cast: Sigourney Weaver stars as a commanding New Republic colonel named Ward, who oversees critical missions following the fall of the Empire. Jeremy Allen White voices the now-grown Rotta the Hutt‚Äîonce Jabba‚Äôs son‚Äîtaking him in a new, muscular gladiator direction. Jonny Coyne returns as the imposing Imperial warlord leading remnants of the Empire, while characters like Garazeb ‚ÄúZeb‚Äù Orrelios and members of the Anzellan species make appearances, deepening the narrative continuity with the Disney+ series.

Scheduled for release on May 22, 2026, "The Mandalorian & Grogu" serves as the first theatrical installment in the Star Wars franchise since The Rise of Skywalker (2019). Although a trailer has not yet been released to the public, exclusive footage debuted at D23 2024 and Star Wars Celebration 2025, offering glimpses of Grogu training, AT-ATs in snowy terrain, and exciting action sequences. Directed and produced by Favreau, with Kathleen Kennedy and Dave Filoni also at the helm, the film promises to deliver a standalone cinematic experience that both longtime fans and newcomers can enjoy.

The enhanced video version of ‚ÄúWe Are The World‚Äù by USA For Africa. Listen to the 40th anniversary remastered audio everywhere at: http://orcd.co/wearetheworldremastered

‚ÄúWe Are The World‚Äù was originally released on March 7, 1985. The song was produced by Quincy Jones and written by Michael Jackson and Lionel Richie. It was recorded in Los Angeles, CA, with Stevie Wonder, Paul Simon, Kenny Rogers, Tina Turner, Billy Joel, Diana Ross, Dionne, Warwick, Bruce Springsteen, Bob Dylan, Ray Charles, Bette Midler, Smokey Robinson, and more.

A remastered and Spatial Audio version of ‚ÄúWe Are The World‚Äù was released on Friday, November 21, 2025 to commemorate 40 years of ‚ÄúWe Are The World.‚Äù

Subscribe for more content from USA For Africa: http://youtube.com/@usaforafricaofficial

Follow USA For Africa:
Instagram: http://instagram.com/usaforafricaofficial
TikTok: http://tiktok.com/@usaforafrica.official
Facebook: http://facebook.com/usaforafricaofficial
Website: http://usaforafrica.org
Facebook: http://facebook.com/usa4africa

Credits:
Music video courtesy of USA For Africa

When we heed a certain call
When the world must come together as one

There are people dying
Oh, and it‚Äôs time to lend a hand to life
The greatest gift of all

We can‚Äôt go on

We are all a part of God‚Äôs great big family
And the truth, you know, love is all we need

We are the world
We are the children
We are the ones to make a brighter day
So let‚Äôs start giving

snippet.title: Minecraft, But We're Chained Together
snippet.description:
Inspired off of the popular video game "Chained Together", we are physically stuck together by a chain! The chain follows ACTUAL physics in Minecraft!

Follow my socials:
‚ûΩ Twitter - @dreamwastaken
‚ûΩ Instagram - @dreamwastaken
‚ûΩ Snapchat - @dreampublic

George: @GeorgeNotFound 
Sapnap: @Sapnap 

This challenge was crazy! It took forever to get the chain physics right. I've seen a lot of other chained together videos in Minecraft, but they were all using leads, or something that didn't have proper chain physics. So we custom coded an awesome mod and decided to give it a try!

It was super funny and a very intense challenge!

We have to beat the game while chained together. Like the video if you want to see more stuff like it!

Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/DreamWasTaken

üé§ Lyrics: Billie Eilish - The 30th 

Sometimes you look the same
Just like you did before the accident
When you're staring into space
It's hard to believe you don't remember it
Woke up in the ambulance
You pieced it all together on the drive
I know you don't remember calling me
But I told you, even then, you looked so pretty
In a hospital bed
I remember you said you were scared
And so was I
In a stand-still on The Five
Thought it was unusually early traffic
Usually, I don't panic
I just wanted to be on time
When I saw the ambulances on the shoulder
I didn't even think of pulling over
I pieced it all together late that night
And I know you don't remember calling me
But I told you, even then, you looked so pretty
In a hospital bed
I remember you said you were scared
And so was I
What if it happened to you on a different day?
On a bridge where there wasn't a rail in the way?
Or a neighborhood street where the little kids play?
Or the Angeles Crest in the snow or the rain?
What if you weren't alone? There were kids in the car
What if you were remote? No one knows where you are
If you changed anything, would you not have survived?
You're alive, you're alive, you're alive
And I know you don't remember calling me
But I told you, even then, you looked so pretty
In your hospital bed
I remember you said you were scared
And so am I

.........

snippet.title: Minecraft But There's Realistic Hearts
snippet.description:
This is Minecraft But There's Realistic Hearts! When Steve's hearts get stolen by the Realistic mobs he needs to defeat them! Steve needs to learn how to be and behave like a realistic character if he wants to use all the new Realistic powers, gadgets, and abilities! Can Steve learn all the secrets and abilities of Realistic hearts, and upgrade into the ultimate realistic character? This is Minecraft But There's Realistic Hearts!
__

üëãüèº Checkpoint Website: https://checkpointmultiverse.com/
üì∏ Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/checkpoint.yt
‚ù§Ô∏è Connect With Us: https://direct.me/checkpointmultiverse
üßëüèº‚Äçü§ù‚Äçüßëüèº Join the Community on Discord: https://discord.gg/jkfV7mSxB6

üéµ Additional Music provided by Epidemic Sound: https://www.epidemicsound.com/

MORE CHECKPOINT ADVENTURES:

‚Ä£ MINECRAFT DIMENSION: https://bit.ly/3mKfUOL


¬¨

Minecraft is an open world game that has no specific goals for the player to accomplish, allowing players a large amount of freedom in choosing how to play the game however, there is an achievement system. The gameplay by default is first person, but players have the option to play in third person mode. The core gameplay revolves around breaking and placing blocks. The game world is essentially composed of rough 3D objects‚Äîmainly cubes‚Äîthat are arranged in a fixed grid pattern and represent different materials, such as dirt, stone, various ores, water, and tree trunks. While players can move freely across the world, objects and items can only be placed at fixed locations relative to the grid. Players can gather these material blocks and place them elsewhere, thus allowing for various constructions.

#Checkpoint #Minecraft

Steve needs to learn how to be and behave like a realistic character if he wants to use all the new Realistic powers, gadgets, and abilities! Can Steve learn all the secrets and abilities of Realistic hearts, and upgrade into the ultimate realistic character? This is Minecraft But There's Realistic Hearts!

MORE CHECKPOINT ADVENTURES:

‚Ä£ MINECRAFT DIMENSION: https://bit.ly/3mKfUOL


¬¨

Minecraft is an open world game that has no specific goals for the player to accomplish, allowing players a large amount of freedom in choosing how to play the game however, there is an achievement system. The gameplay by default is first person, but players have the option to play in third person mode. The core gameplay revolves around breaking and placing blocks. The game world is essentially composed of rough 3D objects‚Äîmainly cubes‚Äîthat are arranged in a fixed grid pattern and represent different materials, such as dirt, stone, various ores, water, and tree trunks. While players can move freely across the world, objects and items can only be placed at fixed locations relative to the grid. Players can gather these material blocks and place them elsewhere, thus allowing for various constructions.

snippet.title: My Genius Gambling Plan FINALLY Worked! ($10,000 WIN)
snippet.description:
We are BACK at the Casino, and my SICK Gambling FINALLY WORKED! We‚Äôre about to go crazy on this vlog to celebrate, LET‚ÄôS GET FIRING! Thank you all for watching! You‚Äôre all beautiful, and I truly appreciate every single one of you for riding along on this crazy journey.  Wish me luck, and I‚Äôll see you in the next one! Let‚Äôs go to war!

Brettski arrived at the Silver Horizon Casino with **$50,000 of pure, unbelievable parlay magic** burning a hole in his pocket. One dollar‚Äîjust one‚Äîhad turned into a miracle after a string of sports outcomes so unlikely that even statisticians were arguing online about whether physics had been involved.

Now he strode through the casino doors like a man carrying destiny on his shoulders. The carpet shimmered. The chandeliers hummed. Machines chirped greetings like they somehow knew what he‚Äôd done.

Brettski headed for the high-stakes section, but before he got there, a dealer from a nearby blackjack table called out, ‚ÄúHey, aren‚Äôt you the guy who hit the Parlay of the Century?‚Äù

He froze. He hadn‚Äôt told anyone. The sportsbook hadn‚Äôt released his name. Yet every head turned toward him with a strange, synchronized eagerness.

Ignoring the prickle on his neck, Brettski sat at a massive, obsidian-black slot machine he‚Äôd never seen before. No branding. No manufacturer tag. Just a single glowing button labeled **BET IT ALL**.

He laughed. ‚ÄúCute.‚Äù
He inserted a few thousand.

The screen flashed red: **INSUFFICIENT COMMITMENT.**

A chill ran through him.

As he hesitated, a sharply dressed stranger in a silver suit appeared at his side. ‚ÄúThe machine only responds to the full amount,‚Äù the man said softly. ‚ÄúFifty thousand‚Ä¶ or nothing.‚Äù

Brettski blinked. ‚ÄúHow do you know how much I have?‚Äù

The man smiled without warmth. ‚ÄúEveryone knows. After all‚Ä¶ that parlay wasn‚Äôt supposed to hit.‚Äù

Before Brettski could reply, the machine sucked the entire stack of cash from his hands with a mechanical inhale. The room dimmed. The reels began spinning violently, symbols melting into each other like liquid metal.

The stranger stepped back and whispered:

**‚ÄúIf it lands on the wrong outcome‚Ä¶ they‚Äôll want their money back.‚Äù**

The first reel stopped. Then the second.

The third reel slowed‚Ä¶ trembling‚Ä¶ on an impossible symbol:
**A photo of Brettski himself.**

#slots #blackjack #gambling #casino #baccarat #roulette

Who is Brettski? Brettski is a Professional Gambler, similar to the ancient legends Vegas Matt, Bluff, DegenDalt, TheBigJackpot, or Lady Luck HQ! However, unlike these legends, Brettski has thousands of years of stored ancient knowledge harvested by the elders, at skills such as Slot Machines, Roulette, Blackjack, Craps, Bubble Craps, Poker, and Baccarat.  Brettski's goal as a Professional Gambler is simple: own all of Las Vegas, using funds made by Gambling.  Subscribe to support his journey in world domination.

id.title: Rencana Perjudian Jenius Saya AKHIRNYA Berhasil! (MENANG $10.000)
id.description:
Kami KEMBALI ke Kasino, dan Perjudianku yang GILA AKHIRNYA BERHASIL! Kami akan menggila di vlog ini untuk merayakannya, AYO KITA BERJUANG! Terima kasih semua sudah menonton! Kalian semua cantik, dan saya sangat menghargai kalian semua yang telah ikut serta dalam perjalanan gila ini. Doakan saya beruntung, dan sampai jumpa di vlog berikutnya! Ayo berperang!

Brettski tiba di Kasino Silver Horizon dengan **$50.000 keajaiban parlay yang murni dan tak terbayangkan** yang membakar kantongnya. Asmongold Clips / Asmongold Reacts To: Asmongold is the 2nd most popular north american streamer in the world for 2025


On this Asmongold Clips Youtube Channel you'll never quit finding all the funny Asmongold Moments with Mcconnell and the best Asmongold Highlights from the most popular games, like: Baldur's Gate 3, Helldivers 2, Starfield, Blizzard Diablo 4, The War Within & Hardcore Classic WoW, the record breaking MMORPG FFXIV, Path of Exile 2, sneak peeks from Gameplay of the upcoming Riot MMO and playthroughs of many other popular games like Monster Hunter, Final Fantasy 16, Elden Ring and more. Also Asmongold Reacts to a lot of content, such as World Record Speed Run of games, Drama and videos of some of the most interesting creators like penguinz0, Internet Historian, Emiru, Dunkey and more. Asmon is also known for his "The True Story of Asmongold", "Asmongold $2 Pizza" and "Asmongold $2 Steak", "Asmongold Room and House Tour" videos, the legendary Transmog Competitions and Mount Off competitions, Ban Appeals, Media Share streams, Reddit Recap Reactions and much more.

‚ñ∫ Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/zackrawrr
